r, this is my first char and I just started playing EQ about a little over a month ago, so I'm clueless about most things.  Im a DE and I threw all my starting points into AGI and DEX, I assumed at the time that that would be useful.  I will also hit lvl 22 tonight.   I constantly get PKd by all classes, even lvl's much lower then me, and only twice have I fought them off cause I was majorly buffed and I think the other person was 4 lvls under me.  My main strategy is bag and zone.  I have never just started the attack either, so I guess I have always been at an initial disadvantage.  But who really wants to try and PK someone and then get whopped up on.  Gear and cash have been big problems for me so far.  From reading and getting PK'd so much, I know resistent gear is important, but that cost money and I only have 60 pp in the bank right now and couldnt risk losing the gear to PC's.  Money is starting to come in a little faster now, but that also mean Im facing higher levels each time too.  Hell, I was using Stilleto of the bloodclaw as my primary wep until lvl 20, then I bought a harpoon of the depths and just moved the stilleto to the other hand.  Alot of my cash so far has been dropped into the trade skills, im a lvl 135 blacksmith so I can make my own banded, and a 56 tailor hoping to make the money bags.  I started the trade skills mainly cause I thought that it would make me money, but that really hasn't been the case.  Also, my armour is all banded except for a split paw mask (+5 MR) and some +2 jewelery.  Any advice would be appreciated ( I just found out about evade yesterday), and I have a couple questions too.  My game name is Vilnayan, so feel free to wave at my corpse as u run by it.  Thanks in advance<br>
<br>
1) NODROP items: I could really use some of this, so my first response isn't to bag.  Is there any NODROP armour within my level range?  I read that Befallen is supposed to drop some prestine leather,  will this be my first option to go for and will I need to wait till 30 to try and get some.  Also, I have read that befallen is back to normal,  what does that mean ?<br>
<br>
2) Mask of deception: Will I have a resonable chance of looting this on my server?  I really dont know that many PC's, so it's really gonna have to be that a group is down there that will let me loot it.  Im already a DE, but I'm pretty sure this is nodrop and MR +7 which is what im looking for.  Please let me know if im wrong. <br>
<br>
3) Poisons: I made my first root poison and it worked great, the guy just gated though so I still owe him 4.  What is going to be the best and cheapest poison that I can farm that will be useful for PvP.  I just collect a stack of asp poison sacks.  So I am thinking blind will be good, but still kinda pricey.<br>
