<br>
Sold in various places around the world for 16pp each has 5 charges of nullify magic that takes a few seconds to cast.  At your lvl you can get rid of the following spells with it<br>
<br>
wizards- root<br>
enchanters- root, all enc dots, spells that lower your str<br>
druids- root, snare, stinging swarm and all dots in that line<br>
necromancers- everything they can cast at your lvl that takes effect over time<br>
rangers-root and snare<br>
shadowknights- darkness(snare basicly)<br>
clerics- root<br>
shamans- root (pumice will not remove any shaman dots)<br>
<br>
